# rSwitch - Reconfigurable Switch (Production Guide)

rSwitch is a lightweight, production-focused implementation of a modular,
programmable XDP-based switch. The authoritative sources are under `rswitch/`:
`rswitch/user/` (loader, tools) and `rswitch/bpf/modules/` (BPF modules).

Quick Links:
